OL,4,CGhana removes 'racist' Gandhi statue
OL,5, A statue of Mahatma Gandhi, the famed
OL,6, Indian independence leader, has been
OL,7, removed from a university campus in
OL,8, Ghana's capital, Accra.
OL,10,FUniversity of Ghana lecturers began a
OL,11,Fpetition for its removal shortly after
OL,12,Fit was unveiled in 2016 by India's
OL,13,Fformer President Pranab Mukherjee.
OL,15,FThe petition said Gandhi was "racist"
OL,16,Fand African heroes should be put first.
OL,18,FIn the wake of the row, Ghana's
OL,19,Fgovernment at the time said the statue
OL,20,Fwould be relocated.
